sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant A as Peer A
  participant EA as SyncEngine A
  participant T as Transport
  participant EB as SyncEngine B
  participant B as Peer B

  A->>EA: dispatch(set key=name value=alice)
  EA->>EA: tickClock(local)
  EA->>EA: build CRDTOperation(id, peerId, clock)
  EA->>T: send(operation)
  EA->>A: emit operation (local observers)

  T->>EB: onReceive(operation)
  EB->>EB: mergeClocks(local, remote)
  EB->>EB: LWW/OR-Set conflict resolution
  EB->>B: emit operation (remote observers)

  B->>EB: dispatch(set key=status value=ok)
  EB->>EB: tickClock(remote)
  EB->>T: send(operation)
  T->>EA: onReceive(operation)
  EA->>EA: mergeClocks(local, remote)
  EA->>A: emit operation (converged state)
